0. Please execute

     `./init.sh`

   to get openvanilla-modules' source code.
   
1. To compile openvanilla-modulesï¼Œplease execute
   
     `cd openvanilla-modules/`
     `./configure --prefix=/usr/` 
     `make`

   P.S. /usr/ can be set to your prefered path.

2. To install, please execute
      
     `make install`

